Type: Package
Package: LLMRagent
Title: Reproducible Language-Model Agents for Research
Version: 0.8.1
Authors@R:
    person("Ali", "Sanaei", , "sanaei@uchicago.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Large language model agents as governed research instruments,
  built on 'LLMR'. An agent's tools and budgets are declared up front, and
  every run carries provenance that can be written as a hash-sealed record
  whose integrity a reviewer can verify.
